headline: Why Incyte (INCY) Stock Is Nosediving
summary: Shares of biopharmaceutical company Incyte Corporation (NASDAQ:INCY) fell 15.2% in the pre-market session after the company released phase three trial data for a skin condition treatment, which fell below Wall Street's expectations. According to the data, the drug was effective for less than half of the participants who took it in the trials.
